==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quinhydrone
<hw>Quin*hy"drone</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Quin</ets>one + <ets>hydro</ets>quinone.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A green crystalline substance formed by the
union of quinone with hydroquinone, or as an intermediate product in the
oxidation of hydroquinone or the reduction of quinone.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>chinhydrone</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quinia</ent>⟦br⟧
